cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with the application of convolutional neural networks to the problems of histology image classification and whole slide image segmentation for breast cancer diagnosis. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of transfer learning also suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The study of various approaches for transfer learning and the use of histology images suggest the involvement of multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
